descriptionHtml:
Want to connect with artists from all over the world from the comfort of your home? Vampr is the number one social network for creatives in the music industry that helps you find people to collaborate with, promote your songs, and distribute your music.

Looking for a new singer for your band, a producer, or simply someone to jam with? Vampr is for you. Vampr helps bring artists together and collaborate regardless of where they are. Get the latest music news and find the best upcoming musicians in a single place.

Want to monetize your work? Publishing and Music Distribution will help you promote and make money from your tracks.

With Vampr you can network with fellow creatives, promote your songs and monetize your music from one single platform.

*Connect: Find and meet musicians, industry professionals, and music lovers
*News: Keep up to date with the latest music news
*Collaborate: Build your network and collaborate with fellow creatives
*Upcoming talent: Find the best upcoming artists
*Monetize your work: Promote your songs and make money from your tracks with Publishing and Music Distribution

Awards & Recognitions

*The Lovie Awards - Community & Social, Winner 2018

*Apple Best of 2017 - Trends of the Year

descriptionHtml:
Vampr is the #1 social network for artists that helps you find people to collaborate with.

Award-winning app: Best of App Store and Fast Company: Most Innovative Companies

Over 1M users and 8M connections.

Vampr has been dubbed the LinkedIn for musicians as it shares each user’s expertise as well as a social media interface with an easy swipe left/right function to connect with others.
- Forbes

Vampr gives user-friendly support for all those songwriters, indie musicians, DJs, rappers, and folk artists, who are struggling to connect and break into the necessary circles they need to.
- HuffPost

Vampr is positioning itself as a LinkedIn for musicians, helping them find one another, collaborate, and even distribute their work.
- FastCompany
WHY VAMPR?

Vampr is the number one social platform helping creatives and artists find people to collaborate with, create new music and monetize their work - an essential network that grows with you every step of your journey.

In our mission to empower independent artists, Vampr also allows you to get your music on all major digital stores (Spotify, Apple Music, TikTok, Amazon Music, and more) with Vampr Distribution as well as place your tracks on film, TV, ads and video games without the need for a publisher with Vampr Publishing.

Vampr also offers an educational platform called Academy that delivers world-class training to help artists turn their passion into a full-time career.

WHAT CAN I DO ON VAMPR?

🔎 DISCOVER
Find musicians, industry professionals and music lovers near you to collaborate with and get discovered. There are over 1M users on Vampr so you’ll find everything from singers to guitarists, audio mixers, composers and a lot more. Hire someone for a gig or find your new band member, the possibilities are endless.

​​💬 CONNECT
Build your network, message your new contacts and stay in touch with your connections.

🎵 CONTROL
From Publishing to Pro to Distribution – we’re here to support you professionally and help you make money from your tracks. With Vampr you have access to publishing and music distribution without having to spend hundreds of dollars on a publisher or distributor.

🤝 COLLABORATE
Work with upcoming artists from all over the world and create new music. Finding musicians and creatives to collaborate with has never been easier.

🎓 LEARN
Vampr Academy delivers world-class training for artists designed to help you develop your skills and advance your career. From courses about the Business of Music to Content Creation for Musicians to Indie Record Label Contracts to NFTs for Artists, Vampr Academy provides you with the tools to turn your passion into a full-time career.
